I see something. There it is!</i>

04:04.417 --> 04:06.127
<i>I think this is it. Right here.</i>

04:07.044 --> 04:10.089
<i>Yeah, this is definitely it.
This is the place.</i>

04:12.425 --> 04:13.759
<i>Jackpot!</i>

04:15.011 --> 04:16.929
<i>Come on, right down here, kids!</i>

04:23.728 --> 04:25.521
<i>Come on, dig in, you kids.</i>

04:26.522 --> 04:27.898
<i>Here we go!</i>

04:28.190 --> 04:30.192
