22:02.203 --> 22:03.496
But I'm not the father.

22:03.662 --> 22:05.831
Nurse, another one's coming.

22:06.082 --> 22:08.042
Deep breaths. Come on.

22:09.919 --> 22:13.047
<i>Okay, this will pass. Watch the head.</i>

22:16.384 --> 22:17.426
I need drugs.

22:17.677 --> 22:20.096
Breathe slower. This isn't aerobics.

22:20.262 --> 22:22.223
Fuck my breathing!

22:22.431 --> 22:26.352
You gotta calm down or I'll have to
get the exorcist in here.

22:26.811 --> 22:27.978
Give me drugs!

22:28.145 --> 22:30.189
No, you don't want drugs.

22:30.398 --> 22:32.400
Yes, I do.
I'm gonna split in two.

22:32.650 --> 22:33.693
Do something.

22:33.943 --> 22:37.405
