-Five, six.

22:56.007 --> 22:57.508
Are we doing our Lamaze?

22:57.717 --> 23:01.095
I'm really trying,
but I dropped out of Lamaze.

23:01.762 --> 23:05.099
But I'll go to summer school
if you make the pain stop.

23:05.808 --> 23:08.102
Demerol to take
the edge off contractions?

23:08.561 --> 23:10.771
Oh, yes, that'd be great.

23:10.980 --> 23:14.525
I'd really like that.
Give me a lot of it so it doesn't...

23:14.734 --> 23:17.611
...wear off
in the middle of the birth.

23:17.862 --> 23:19.488
Give me more than usual...

23:19.697 --> 23:22.658
...because I'm in more pain
than most of your patients.

23:23.617 --> 23:25.661
How long before it kicks in?

23:25.828 --> 23:29.373
-Give me enough that it'll last.
-Hold on, there we go.

23:29.540 --> 23:31.042
There we go.

23:31.292 --> 23:33.627
Thank you a really lot.

23:35.463 --> 23:38.799
<i>Now that is a little more like it.</i>

23:40.134 --> 23:42.636
<i>Hey, here's Mr Hand here.</i>

23:44.680 --> 23:48.142
<i>Now, that is very cosmic.
I don't understand.</i>

23:50.686 --> 23:52.980
<i>What's that little light down there?</i>

23:55.941 --> 23:57.735
That's it, breathe.

23:59.945 --> 24:01.614
That's it. Thattagirl.

24:01.781 --> 24:04.367
Push. One more.

24:04.867 --> 24:07.661
<i>Don't push. Stop with the pushing.
I'm falling!</i>

24:14.877 --> 24:16.712
<i>Help! Help!</i>

24:16.879 --> 24:20.341
<i>Oh, no, put me back in.
Put me back in, please.</i>

24:20.591 --> 24:22.927
<i>Let go of my head and put me back in!</i>

24:23.094 --> 24:24.804
It's a boy.

24:25.471 --> 24:27.473
<i>Who's that? Who's that?</i>

24:28.140 --> 24:30.559
<i>Who are you? Oh, no!</i>

24:30.810 --> 24:33.896
<i>Lady, I'm freezing. I'm so cold.</i>

24:34.105 --> 24:37.108
<i>Let's be reasonable.
Get that thing away from me.</i>

24:37.400 --> 24:39.026
Do you want to do the cord?

24:39.276 --> 24:41.946
<i>-Don't give that to him.
</i>-You take this one.

24:42.154 --> 24:44.115
<i>Let's talk about-- I need that!</i>

24:46.575 --> 24:50.579
<i>Lady, you in the grey, a blanket,
